div.connect-container
  h3 Connect
  hr
  div.connect-navigation
    ul.nav.nav-tabs
      li.active
        a(href=".registered", data-toggle="tab", aria-expanded="true") Registered Users
      li
        a(href=".new", data-toggle="tab", aria-expanded="true") New Users
  div#connectContent.tab-content
    div.registered.tab-pane.fade.active.in
      div.row
        div.col-md-12.connect-helper
          div.row
            div.col-md-12
              h4.text-left Find your Honey
              p In order to get the most out of the honeydoo list, invite your better half to join.
          div.row
            div.col-md-6
              h5.text-left Assign and share
              p The point here is connect, share, and help organize your life and relationship. While your at it, earn points when you accomplish goals.
            div.col-md-6
              h5.text-left Search and get started
              p If your honey is already a registered user, use the search feature below, find your mate, and add them. It's that easy!
      div.row
        div.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2.panel-container
          div.panel.panel-default
            div.panel-heading
              h5.text-center Search for you honey:
            div.panel-body
              div.text-center(ng-show="disable")
                p You are currently connected, or have a pending connection status. Check you notifications.
                p To disconnect with you current honey, visit your account settings
                  a(ui-sref="home.edit_profile") &nbsp;here.
              div.row()
                div.col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
                  //div.form-group
                  //  selectpicker(data-array="selectData", data-disable="disable", change-disable="changeDisable()", ng-model="myModel") {{myModel}}
                  angucomplete-alt(id="searchHoney", placeholder="Honey Search", pause="200", selected-object="selectedUser", title-field="firstname,lastname", image-field="img", description-field="un", local-data="users", local-search="honeySearch", minlength="0", input-class="form-control", disable-input="disable")
                  p {{selectedUser.description}}
            div.panel-footer(ng-hide="disable || !honey")
              div.confirm-send-container.text-center
                p Confirm your request to invite {{honey}} to join you:
                button.btn(type="button", ng-click="!disable && setInviteStatus()") Send request!
    div.new.tab-pane.fade
      div.row
        div.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
          h4.text-center Invite your honey to join!
          p If you can't locate your honey or they haven't registered with Honeydoo List, feel free to use our invitation service.
          p Just include their email address in the input below and press send. They should receive your request to join immediately!
      div.row
        div.col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
          div.panel.panel-default
            div.panel-heading
              h5.text-center Invite your honey to join now:
            div.panel-body
              div.text-center(ng-show="disable")
                p You are currently connected, or have a pending connection status. Check you notifications.
                p To disconnect with you current honey, visit your account settings
                  a(ui-sref="home.edit_profile") &nbsp;here.
              div.row
                div.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
                  div.input-group
                    input.form-control(type="text", placeholder="Email address", ng-disabled="disable")
                    span.input-group-btn
                      button.btn.btn-secondary(type="submit", ng-disabled="disable") Go!




